    "comment": "Rationale: Figure 4: Electron micrographs of the stratum radiatum of the hippocampal CA1 region showing immunoparticles for Rgs7, as detected using a pre-embedding immunogold method. Synaptic localization was mostly to postsynapses with sparse labeling (5% of total particles) at presynaptic sites. Futher, extensive dendritic labeling was observed.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Six young adult (P30) OF-1 mice obtained from the Animal House Facility at the School of Medicine of the University of Castilla-La Mancha were used in immunohistochemical experiments at the light and electron microscopic level.\"\n\n\"Affinity-purified rabbit anti-Rgs7 and rabbit anti-Gβ5 were generated and characterized previously (Cao et al., 2008; Xie et al., 2012).\" PMID:18842904 PMID:21766168",
